        "\n",
        "| Model | Accuracy | Accuracy (10-CV) |\n",
        "| ---   | --- | --- |\n",
        "| Baseline   | 0.08943089430894309   |  0.08669010923238066  |\n",
        "| KNN   |0.975609756097561 |0.9920656890617986 |\n",
