    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "0f-ED39fqrV1"
      },
      "source": [
        "### Hyper parameter optimization\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Train a KNN model for different values of *n_neighbors* and plot its accuracy."
      ]
    },
